Russia 1 presenter Olga Skabeyeva, who is a vocal supporter of the war in Ukraine said that the sinking of the missile cruiser meant that the "special military operation" had escalated to a new level. She added that Moscow is now effectively at war with NATO. This follows the news that Finland's Europe Minister said Finland is "highly likely" to join NATO despite Russia's threats to launch nuclear weapons at the Baltic if it does so.   FOLLOW BELOW FOR LIVE UPDATES... 